== ezftpsearch
== Development version, not suitable for use.

Description goes here


== REQUIREMENT

1 RAILS 2.1 for bigint (ftpentry size)
2 ftp server should support command 'OPTS UTF8 ON' with non-ASCII file names

== NOTE
1 Use this command to view rake task's usage FIRST.
  rake -D ezftpsearch

2 ONLY Unix type of FTP is finished and tested. Other type of ftps should modify first.

